{"tid":1589713,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"華記搞到日本社區污煙瘴氣，得罪本地人","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T17:01:54.000Z","uid":263557,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8c569de071c9fe1e75a8bb4d301d5a11270091","tid":1589713,"uid":263557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"雖然都兩年前單野，<br />\n但有冇日本手足跟進，去佢附近警局相談下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正華記開到邊都肯定係咁撚樣唔會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單翻譯，<br />\n華記班撚屌搞到周街垃圾，連玻璃都周地扔<br />\n搞到留言個日本妹受傷<br />\n<br />\n店員冇禮貌連歡迎都唔會講，仲係正鋪頭門口食煙<br />\n令附近衛生情況差到仆街<br />\n又完全無視督導員勸告，唔作改善<br />\n得罪晒啲日本街坊<br />\n<br />\n最仆街係華記打住我地香港名義，影衰晒我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbjLL6Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbjLL6Y.png&h=68d7cff9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRutkj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRutkj.png&h=95051556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"768bb5cff0736e954a0c36c95dcbb3cb63f0b04c","tid":1589713,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"4f2b221c78c414685bdad909a9f84a2cbdcba693","tid":1589713,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:42:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾光頭佬<br />\n<br />\n[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid